Package pl.lipiec.Controllers

Class BaseController

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.lipiec.Controllers.BaseController
  • public class BaseController
extends Object
    Singleton base controller used to handle views and controllers This class consists of static fields and methods. Contains instance of current window, view and user logged to the program.
    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Krzysztof Lipiec
